quran[8{c,v,t}:
6,28,"Dur haqeeqat yeh ba t- woh mehez is wajah se kahin ge ke jis haqeeqat par unhon ne parda daal rakha tha woh is waqt be naqaab ho kar un ke samnay aa chuki hogi, warna agar inhen sabiq zindagi ki taraf wapas bheja jaye to phir wohi sab kuch karen jis se inhen mana kya gaya hai, woh to hain hi jhutay ( is liye apni is khwahish ke izhaar mein bhi jhoot hi se kaam len ge )"
6,29,aaj yeh log kehte hain ke zindagi jo kuch bhi hai bas yahi duniya ki zindagi hai aur hum marnay ke baad hargiz dobarah nah uthaye jayen ge
6,30,"kash woh manzar tum dekh sakuu jab yeh apne rab ke samnay kharray kiye jayen ge is waqt un ka rab un se pouchye ga"" kya yeh haqeeqat nahi hai ?"" yeh kahin ge"" haan ae hamaray rab! yeh haqeeqat hi hai"" woh farmaiye ga"" acha! to ab apne inkaar haqeeqat ki Padaash mein azaab ka maza chako """
6,31,"nuqsaan mein par gay woh log jinhon ne Allah se apni mulaqaat ki ittila ko jhoot qarar diya jab achanak woh gharri aa jaye gi to yahi log kahin ge"" afsos! hum se is maamla mein kaisi taqseer hui"" aur inn ka haal yeh hoga ke apni pithon par apne gunaaho ka boojh lade hue hon ge dekho! kaisa bura boojh hai jo yeh utha rahay hain"
6,32,"duniya ki zindagi to aik khail aur aik tamasha hai, haqeeqat mein akhirat hi ka maqam unn logon ke liye behtar hai jo zayan kaari se bachna chahtay hain, phir kya tum log aqal se kaam nah lau ge ?"
6,33,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! hamein maloom hai ke jo baatein yeh log banatay hain un se tumhe ranj hota hai, lekin yeh log tumhe nahi jutlatay balkay yeh zalim darasal Allah ki ayaat ka inkaar kar rahay hain"
6,34,"tum se pehlay bhi bohat se rasooljhutla-ay ja chuke hain, magar is tkzib par aur unn aziyatoon par jo inhen pohanchai gayeen, unhon ne sabr kya, yahan taq ke inhen hamari madad poanch gayi Allah ki baton ko badalny ki taaqat kisi mein nahi hai, aur pichlle Rasolo-n ke sath jo kuch paish aaya is ki khabrain tumhe poanch hi chuki hain"
6,35,"taham agar un logon ki be rukhi tum se bardasht nahi hoti to agar tum mein kuch zor hai to zameen mein koi surang dhuundo ya aasman mein seerhi lagao aur un ke paas koi nishani laane ki koshish karo agar Allah chahta to un sab ko hadaayat par jama kar sakta tha, lehaza nadaan mat bano"
